data.title: Las Consecuencias (Short 2019)
data.meta_description: Las Consecuencias: Directed by Ishtiyak Ahmad Zihad. With Rezaul Karim Shaon. The moving nature of an artist's life is not very beautiful. But the main point of this film is that when a viewer watches the film, he will give his own interpretation which would be logical when compared with the film.
